2.caption: 1962 East–West Pro Bowl
2.description: The 1962 Pro Bowl was the National Football League's twelfth annual all-star game which featured the outstanding performers from the 1961 season. The game was played on January 14, 1962, at the Los Angeles Memorial Coliseum in Los Angeles, California in front of 57,409 fans.
2.inspected:Co-MVPs: Jim Brown (Cleveland Browns), Henry Jordan (Green Bay Packers)
